    n=5: (1/2)^5 = 0.031250 (3.12%)
    n=6: (1/2)^6 = 0.015625 (1.56%)
    n=7: (1/2)^7 = 0.007812 (0.78%)

  x=1: ratio = (2/3)^n
    n=1: (2/3)^1 = 0.666667 (66.67%)
    n=2: (2/3)^2 = 0.444444 (44.44%)
    n=3: (2/3)^3 = 0.296296 (29.63%)
    n=4: (2/3)^4 = 0.197531 (19.75%)
    n=5: (2/3)^5 = 0.131687 (13.17%)
    n=6: (2/3)^6 = 0.087791 (8.78%)
    n=7: (2/3)^7 = 0.058528 (5.85%)

  x=2: ratio = (3/4)^n
    n=1: (3/4)^1 = 0.750000 (75.00%)
    n=2: (3/4)^2 = 0.562500 (56.25%)
